Package: rpptx
Title: Create, Read, and Update PowerPoint Presentations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Mark", "Heckmann", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "heckmann.mark@gmail.com")
Description: Create, read, and update PowerPoint (.pptx) files. An R port of
    the Python 'python-pptx' library. Provides an R6-based object model for
    manipulating presentations, slides, shapes, text, charts, tables, and
    formatting properties.
